==>OBSERVATION: Moonlit Chamber
Moonlight diffuses through the walls, tracing out unreadable sigils in calligraphies of light and dark. Upwards, the sky is open to your eyes. Stairs adorned with bas-relief motifs spiral downward.

Wind flings itself up the walls and toward the sky; you have but to look up.
